      <title>以色列加强对黎巴嫩南部真主党目标的袭击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/israel-steps-up-attacks-on-hezbollah-targets-in-south-lebanonon</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列周一早上加强了对黎巴嫩南部真主党的空袭，并敦促平民撤离该地区。]]></description>
